description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for a Senior Python AI / GenAI Engineer.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Design and develop AI/ML and GenAI applications using Python;
* Build and deploy LLM\\-powered solutions including RAG, multi\\-agent systems, and autonomous AI agents;
* Develop Document Intelligence pipelines (PDF, Office files, structured/unstructured data);
* Implement semantic search and vector\\-based retrieval;
* Design and deploy intelligent chatbots with contextual memory;
* Develop Agent AI systems using LangChain and LangGraph;
* Implement Model Context Protocol (MCP) based integrations for secure AI\\-tool interaction;
* Build REST APIs using FastAPI/Flask for AI services;
* Integrate OpenAI/Azure OpenAI and enterprise data sources;
* Deploy AI applications on Azure/AWS with CI/CD and monitoring;









**Profile:** 



* Bachelor or Master degree;
* \\+8 years of relevant experience;
* Strong proficiency in Python;
* Experience with LangChain, LangGraph, Agent frameworks;
* Hands\\-on experience in RAG architectures and vector databases;
* Experience with OpenAI / Azure OpenAI APIs;
* Knowledge of Document Intelligence \\& NLP;
* Prompt engineering and LLM optimization;
* API development and microservices architecture;
* Cloud deployment experience (Azure preferred);
* Experience building enterprise AI copilots;
* Exposure to multi\\-agent orchestration systems;
* Knowledge of MCP architecture;
* Experience integrating AI with SharePoint/Dataverse;
* Understanding of AI governance and performance evaluation;
* Experience with Azure cloud infrastructure and deployment of scalable applications is nice to have;
* Fluent in English;
